---
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    primaryColor: "#0969da"
    primaryTextColor: "#ffffff"
    primaryBorderColor: "#0550ae"
    lineColor: "#57606a"
    secondaryColor: "#f6f8fa"
    tertiaryColor: "#ddf4ff"
    background: "#ffffff"
    fontSize: "14px"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI Agent
    participant MCP as McpServer
    participant WS as Workspace
    Note over Agent,WS: Session Start
    Agent->>MCP: Read AGENTS-README-FIRST.yaml
    MCP-->>Agent: API key, base URL, workspace path
    Note over Agent,WS: Context Retrieval
    Agent->>MCP: POST /mcpserver/context/search
    MCP->>WS: FTS5 + HNSW vector search
    WS-->>MCP: Matching code chunks
    MCP-->>Agent: Ranked context pack
    Note over Agent,WS: Task Management
    Agent->>MCP: GET /mcpserver/todo?section=backlog
    MCP-->>Agent: TODO item list
    Agent->>MCP: PUT /mcpserver/todo/{id}
    MCP->>WS: Write TODO.yaml / SQLite
    MCP-->>Agent: Updated item
    Note over Agent,WS: Session Logging
    Agent->>MCP: POST /mcpserver/sessionlog
    MCP->>WS: Persist session entry
    MCP-->>Agent: Session ID confirmed
    Note over Agent,WS: GitHub Sync
    Agent->>MCP: POST /mcpserver/sync
    MCP->>WS: Sync TODOs with GitHub Issues
    MCP-->>Agent: Sync result
